_sText: A pack of door prefabs for your maps :D CONTAINS 6 DOORS: door_a - Regular func_door_rotating door door_b - Same as door_a, but with a window :o door_c - small sliding door that moves upwards door_d - double automatic doors door_e - 'floor' door, with button. Could be used as a trap? ;) door_f - large double automatic doors If/when I get more time, I'll add more doors to the pack :P
